  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study was to assess the feasibility and effectiveness of using a
      statewide immunization information system (IIS) to send seasonal influenza vaccine reminders
      from Local Health Departments (LHDs), targeting children with high-risk conditions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
