    <measure>seasonal influenza vaccination</measure>
    <time_frame>up to 4 months following reminder notification</time_frame>
    <description>Receipt of 1 or more dose of seasonal influenza vaccine, either trivalent inactivated influenza vaccine (TIV) or live attenuated influenza vaccine (LAIV)</description>
